Name: M Solutions Partners LLC
NAICS Info: [{'NAICS Code': '541512', 'Description': 'Computer Systems Design Services', 'Capability': "Capabilities Narrative for M Solution Partners  M Solution Partners is a leading consulting and technology firm that specializes in providing solutions based on Microsoft technologies and COBOL. Our team of experienced consultants and developers offer.  a wide range of capabilities to help our clients achieve their business objectives.  Our Capabilities include:  Microsoft Technologies: We specialize in developing solutions based on Microsoft technologies such as .NET, SharePoint, C#, Dynamics 365, and Power Platform. Our team of developers use the latest tools and best practices to deliver high-quality applications that are reliable, scalable, and secure.  COBOL Modernization: M Solution Partners capitalizes on Microsoft's cloud modernization infrastructures to help our clients modernize their legacy COBOL applications. Our team of experts use modernization techniques such as re-hosting, re-engineering, and refactoring to transform legacy COBOL applications into modern, cloud-based solutions. M Solution helps clients seamlessly migrate from COBOL to Microsoft modern technologies, unlocking enhanced efficiency and scalability. Leveraging services such as Azure App Service, Azure Functions, and Azure Kubernetes Service, M Solution enables businesses to modernize their applications. Microsoft's advanced security measures ensure the protection of sensitive data. With M Solution's expertise in Microsoft cloud modernization, businesses can confidently embrace the digital era, accelerating their transformation journey and realizing sustainable success. Cloud Services: We provide cloud-based solutions based on Microsoft Azure that are designed to help our clients reduce costs, increase efficiency, and improve collaboration. We offer a range of cloud services, including infrastructure-as-a-service (IaaS), platform-as-a-service (PaaS), and software-as-a-service (SaaS).  Data Analytics: We help our clients leverage the power of data to make informed business decisions. Our team of data analysts use advanced analytics tools to extract insights from large datasets, helping clients to identify trends, patterns, and opportunities.  Digital Transformation: We help our clients embrace digital technologies to transform their businesses. Our team of experts work with clients to design and implement digital strategies that drive innovation and improve customer experiences.  IT Consulting: We provide IT consulting services that help clients optimize their IT infrastructure, reduce costs, and improve performance. Our team of experts work with clients to identify areas for improvement, develop solutions, and implement best practices.  Project Management: We provide project management services to ensure that our clients’ projects are delivered on time, within budget, and to the highest quality. Our team of project managers work closely with clients to understand their needs, develop project plans, and oversee project execution."}]
